        "content": "<p>Alternative automation:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">theorem</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">thm2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℝ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"bp\">^</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"bp\">^</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"bp\">^</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">=-</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">field_simp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">linear_combination</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
